snippet.title: Kingdom Conquest - Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
Kingdom Conquest is not rated by the ESRB.

Kingdom Conquest is a free-to-play MMO built exclusively for the iPhone & iPod Touch that puts players in the shoes of an adventurer aspiring to become the new king of Magna Gul, the land of monsters. Chaos has spread like wildfire following the disappearance of the former ruler, El Dor, and his empty throne lies open for the taking...
